{"tid":290512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"瓦姆比爾去世　當奴侵形容北韓為殘暴政權","createTime":"2017-06-19T22:43:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-20T07:27:30.000Z","uid":20933,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"195317868a5ca1171ddcfe0b292d473702ada0e8","tid":290512,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T22:43:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/20/064313_da9bda348f471efbfe8106adb8a74500.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F20%2F064313_da9bda348f471efbfe8106adb8a74500.jpg&h=6fa25d16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在北韓被囚禁超過15個月、上星期獲釋回國的22歲美國大學生瓦姆比爾逝世。總統特朗普形容北韓是殘暴政權。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在白宮出席一項活動時說，很多糟糕的事情發生，但起碼把瓦姆比爾送回家，帶到父母身邊。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在另一項聲明中，向瓦姆比爾的家人致以最深切慰問。"},{"pid":"3c2be6cdc10f615fbe1b276f0eb572056d5229e8","tid":290512,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T22:43:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1337051-20170620.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1337051-20170620.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=97CKOxnr0FJNsqoxZB7PGfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=b31a1481\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1337051-20170620.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=8d516025\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1337051-20170620.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"d5dabc170038dbe79207956e18a6bcc01a8493d0","tid":290512,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T22:44:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"30102796cd08eec03ee70e2f39d9ec58f9d1a875","tid":290512,"uid":72197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T22:45:11.000Z","msg":"手多咁就一世"},{"pid":"3c2c320546f0936e2cea8e13a23d3942b4174991","tid":290512,"uid":51978,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"cited